{"tid":1931960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：因急事到珠海已返港　今日起自我隔離14日","createTime":"2020-03-18T12:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T12:59:26.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65927a5b911bb47f1dc1d92c890029e97db4582e","tid":1931960,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員葉劉淑儀在社交網站表示，昨天因急事到珠海，現時已返港，今天開始將在家自我隔離14日，直至4月1日才會回到辦公室工作及出席活動。她表示，已知會立法會及行政會議，期間會在家處理公務，如常工作。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，途經港珠澳大橋回港期間，車輛零星疏落，對受疫情影響變得冷清，感到可惜。她相信，一切活動只是受疫情強行壓抑而停擺，待疫情過去後，將恢復頻繁往來，被壓抑的需求亦會急劇爆發。"},{"pid":"e7b238c0592b6025f4b482717137833a93bfa800","tid":1931960,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68840d34972e626cc82ffad19ac458706c0207cd","tid":1931960,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"專車去專車返都驚??<br />\n<br />\n分明係故意放假"},{"pid":"3bcdf5fbb42a50b5b7415c27e8bef8e4cdd12d52","tid":1931960,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68840d34972e626cc82ffad19ac458706c0207cd","tid":1931960,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"專車去專車返都驚??<br />\n<br />\n分明係故意放假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"大陸返黎要強制14日"},{"pid":"619f1b15e6c7e116506ad53a682d6d9606c6109b","tid":1931960,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a2107e6f821ffae4f05895f4f1d3af0b1747cd","tid":1931960,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"葉劉滅黨都未夠 要自滅全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c158c6658f60279952b62d7a11e26014711bc